latestIgtvVideos.title: Shiv ♥️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Main aur mera pariwar Shiv ki shaayari aur gaane sunnte sunnte bade hue hain. Mere dad unke sabse bade fan hain, aur premi bhi.
Har saal Shiv ke janamdin par ek event organise karte the, jahaan unke writer and poets friends aur Shiv Kumar Batalvi ke puraane dost bhi aate the. Vahaan bas Shiv ki baatein hoti thi, unki kitaabon ki, unki kavitaaon ki, unki zindagi ki. Performances bhi hoti thi. Kuchh log Shiv ke geet gaate the toh kuchh mere jaisa ek unke gaane par naach kar perform karta tha. (Shiv ke sabse bade admirer ki beti bhi toh thi main)
Ek alag sa rishta ban gaya tha Shiv ke saath. Meri zindagi ke har guzarte saal mujhe Shiv thoda sa aur samajh mein aane lagta hai, obviously, Dad jitna nahi :)
Pata nahi kyun kuchh saalon se dad unka janamdin ab akele hi manaate hain, bass unki kitaabon ke saath.
Jald kabhi Shiv se mulaakaat bhi hogi, yakeen hai.
Happy birthday Shiv ♥️
